title: Bobby Talks Controversy With Blake Shelton + Do Dan+Shay Have Unreleased Music In The Vault? + Lunchbox Calls To Confess Past Crimes
itunes:title: Bobby Talks Controversy With Blake Shelton + Do Dan+Shay Have Unreleased Music In The Vault? + Lunchbox Calls To Confess Past Crimes
description:
Bobby talks with Blake Shelton about the controversy surrounding his brand-new song “Minimum Wage”. We also catch up with Dan+Shay to about their No. 1’s, how Shay manages to hit high notes and if they have enough music in the vault in case something ever happened to them. Plus, Lunchbox calls up businesses to confess to crimes he committed as a kid!
